OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774015868
OL,3,CMarwell Zoo asks public for help to
OL,4,Cfind escaped capybara
OL,6,FMarwell Zoo has asked members of the
OL,7,Fpublic to be on the lookout after a
OL,8,Fcapybara escaped from its enclosure
OL,9,Fearlier this week.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the zoo said the
OL,12,Fanimal, named Samba, had most recently
OL,13,Fbeen spotted in the village of
OL,14,FOwslebury - just over two miles away -
OL,15,Fon Wednesday evening.
OL,17,FThe mischievous animal had only
OL,18,Farrived at Marwell, along with another
OL,19,Ffemale capybara, named Tango, on
OL,20,FMonday from Jimmy's Farm & Wildlife
OL,21,FPark, in Suffolk.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
