PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774015868
OL,3,CMarwell Zoo asks public for help to
OL,4,Cfind escaped capybara
OL,6,FSamba and Tango were being held in a
OL,7,Ftemporary holding area, where they
OL,8,Fboth managed to escape on Tuesday.
OL,10,FZookeepers were able to quickly locate
OL,11,Fand retrieve Tango, but Samba was
OL,12,F"more adventurous", the zoo said, and
OL,13,Fevaded capture.
OL,15,F"Our dedicated team began searching
OL,16,Fthe zoo and surrounding area, as well
OL,17,Fas quickly securing the area where
OL,18,Fthey escaped," Marwell Zoo said in a
OL,19,Fstatement.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
