PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774015868
OL,3,CMarwell Zoo asks public for help to
OL,4,Cfind escaped capybara
OL,6,F"Local authorities were informed in
OL,7,Fline with the conditions of our zoo
OL,8,Flicense. As always, animal welfare is
OL,9,Four highest priority, and our team are
OL,10,Fworking hard to bring Samba back as
OL,11,Fquickly and safely as possible."
OL,13,FCapybara's are intelligent, gentle
OL,14,Fanimals, which do not pose a risk to
OL,15,Fthe public, according to the zoo, but
OL,16,Fanyone who spots Samba is strongly
OL,17,Fadvised to not approach her to avoid
OL,18,Fcausing any distress.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
