PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774015868
OL,3,CMarwell Zoo asks public for help to
OL,4,Cfind escaped capybara
OL,6,FUnder no circumstances should a member
OL,7,Fof the public try to capture her by
OL,8,Fthemselves.
OL,10,FThe zoo is asking anyone who walks or
OL,11,Fdrives in the local area to be
OL,12,Fparticularly observant and to check
OL,13,Fponds or local waterways as capybaras
OL,14,Flove to spend time in water.
OL,16,FAny sightings should be immediately
OL,17,Freported on 07436167401.
OL,18,FAlternatively, you can send a photo
OL,19,Fwith location, using Google maps or
OL,20,FWhat3Words.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
